data.description: Beautiful all-brick 2-story home with large, full basement!! Lots of room in this 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath home with a den/office that could be used as a 3rd bedroom. There is also a sunroom/4 seasons room that is quite spacious. The Hardwood floors in this home are beautiful, sturdy and solid and easily restorable to their former luster. The roof is only 3-4 years old and is in fantastic condition. The furnace works well but the ac is not working as of now, but could easily be repaired as needed. Both bedrooms are large and both are located upstairs. The office/den area is located on the mail level. Basement is large enough to put in a couple more bedrooms and a bathroom in if you wanted, and has already had some waterproofing work done recently.  There is a beautiful fireplace in the living room (though the current owners never used it). Outside , there is a beautiful, large, fully fenced backyard perfect for pets or children or just for enjoying nature and being outside in privacy. Across the street, you have beautiful views of a wide open field! This is a great home in a nice neighborhood with a great location - minutes to highways, shopping, restaurants, hospitals and schools! Home could use some love, but is ready for someone to move right in without much work needing to be done. This is an amazing house at an even better price! Come see it today.
